Package org.grouplens.lenskit.data.source

Support for data sources, packaged configurations of DAOs.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataSource
    Representation of a single data source.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDataSource
    Base class to help implement data sources.
    CSVDataSourceBuilder
    Simplified builder that returns a CSV data source (or delimited with another delimiter).
    DefaultDataSourceSpecHandler
    Spec handler for the default LensKit data sources.
    GenericDataSource
    Generic data source backed by a single DAO object, implementing at least EventDAO.
    PackedDataSource
    Data source backed by a packed rating file.
    PackedDataSourceBuilder
    Builder for PackedDataSources.
    TextDataSource
    Data source backed by a CSV file.
    TextDataSourceBuilder
    Builder for text file data sources.

Package org.grouplens.lenskit.data.source Description

Support for data sources, packaged configurations of DAOs. These objects package up one or more data access objects that together comprise the data source for a recommendation run.
